http://www.sohu.com/a/424881913_114988	35622
<p><img src="//p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201015/3b595a104c8d46ada32f8d7fdc33d0db.jpeg" width="626" height="823.19" /></p>
<p>《金刚川》提档海报。</p>
